item.dc:creator: ramiz
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)

...or something like this:

The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.

As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Privacy Policy
item.dc:creator: ramiz
item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Suggested text: Our website address is: https://rms-cleaning.com.

Comments

Suggested text: When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.

An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.

Media

Suggested text: If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.

Cookies

Suggested text: If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.

If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.

When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select "Remember Me", your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.

If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.

Embedded content from other websites

Suggested text: Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.

These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.

Who we share your data with

Suggested text: If you request a password reset, your IP address will be included in the reset email.

How long we retain your data

Suggested text: If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.

For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.

What rights you have over your data

Suggested text: If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.

Where your data is sent

Suggested text: Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.

Welcome To RMS Cleaning

When It Comes To Cleanliness, you deserve nothing but the finest.

RMS Cleaning is a fully insured residential and commercial cleaning company based in New Jersey.

Get A Free Quote

(267) 641-5137

rmscleaning0@gmail.com

On call 24/7

About Us

RMS Cleaning is a distinguished family-owned cleaning business based in New Jersey. RMS Cleaning is dedicated to providing reliable, high-quality cleaning services with a strong focus on customer satisfaction and competitive pricing. The company offers a comprehensive range of services, including residential, commercial, deep cleaning, and move-in/move-out cleaning, all utilizing eco-friendly products.

Read More

We provide these cleaning services

Deep Cleaning

Top-to-bottom cleaning: baseboards, inside appliances, detailed dusting, floor care.

Move-In / Move-Out Cleaning

Full clean of vacant properties: cabinets, closets, drawers, kitchens, bathrooms.

Standard/Recurring Cleaning

Maintenance cleaning (weekly/bi-weekly/monthly): kitchens, baths, floors, surfaces, trash removal.

Airbnb Turnover Cleaning

Between-guest clean: trash removal, bed making with your linens, surface wipe-downs. Laundry optional.

RV Deep Cleaning

Interior detailing of RVs up to 45?: kitchen, bathroom, floors, seating, sleeping areas, windows, vents.

Office & Commercial Cleaning

Dusting, vacuuming/mopping, restroom sanitation, trash/recycling removal, break room/kitchen cleaning.

Read More

Grow Your Vision

At RMS Cleaning LLC, we are committed to providing superior, eco-friendly cleaning services that maintain the pristine condition of your spaces while prioritizing environmental sustainability.

As a family-owned business with a strong commitment to excellence, we bring over a decade of expertise and unwavering dedication to every project we undertake. Whether you require residential cleaning or commercial cleaning services, our team of professionals is devoted to delivering exceptional, sustainable cleaning solutions tailored to your specific needs

Read More

Testimonials

Jayson Eniore New York

RMS Cleaning has been a game-changer for my business. Their attention to detail and reliability means I can focus on running my business without worrying about cleanliness. They are always on time and their team is very trustworthy. Absolutely the best cleaning service in Trenton!

Louis Pete New York

I hired RMS Cleaning for a deep clean of my home before a big family event, and they exceeded my expectations. The attention to detail was incrediblemy kitchen and bathrooms have never looked better. The staff was friendly and punctual. Will definitely use them again!

Andy B New York

We use RMS Cleaning for our commercial property, and their service is top-notch. The team is always professional and does a thorough job every time. Our office looks immaculate, and weve received compliments from clients about how clean it is. Great service at a reasonable price!

Marie Beaubrun New York

Made appt late Monday afternoon. The crew showed up weds morning. Three very respectful workers showed up with all gear and supplies needed They did the initial clean then went back thru and treated each spot until it was removed They also were very thorough with removing the odors. They were quick yet thorough and again super friendly. Would absolutely recommend

frequently Ask Question

What areas do you serve?

New Jersey, Pennsylvania, and New York.

Are you insured?

Yes, RMS Cleaning is fully insured.

Do you bring supplies?

Yes, we provide all professional-grade supplies and equipment.

Do recurring clients get a discount?

Yes, recurring clients receive a discount on our standard rates.

Do you offer steam cleaning or hoarder cleanings?

Yes, we offer both steam cleaning and hoarder cleaning services.

How do I get a quote?

Send your address, # of beds & baths, cleaning type, and photos via text (267) 641-5137 or email. Quotes returned same day.

Are you available 24/7?

Yes, were on call 24/7, though we do not work Fri night or Sat until after sunset.

Can I book a weekend cleaning?

Yes, Sat evenings and all day Sun. Unavailable Sat morning & afternoon.

Im a federal clienthow do I arrange services?

Federal clients should email or call RMS Cleaning to discuss contract terms and scheduling.

Welcome To RMS Cleaning

BBC accredited

When It Comes To Cleanliness, you deserve nothing but the finest.

RMS Cleaning is a fully insured residential and commercial cleaning company based in New Jersey.

Get A Free Quote

(267) 641-5137

rmscleaning0@gmail.com

On call 24/7

About Us

RMS Cleaning is a distinguished family-owned cleaning business based in New Jersey. RMS Cleaning is dedicated to providing reliable, high-quality cleaning services with a strong focus on customer satisfaction and competitive pricing. The company offers a comprehensive range of services, including residential, commercial, deep cleaning, and move-in/move-out cleaning, all utilizing eco-friendly products.

Read More

We provide these cleaning services

Deep Cleaning

Top-to-bottom cleaning: baseboards, inside appliances, detailed dusting, floor care.

Move-In / Move-Out Cleaning

Full clean of vacant properties: cabinets, closets, drawers, kitchens, bathrooms.

Standard/Recurring Cleaning

Maintenance cleaning (weekly/bi-weekly/monthly): kitchens, baths, floors, surfaces, trash removal.

Airbnb Turnover Cleaning

Between-guest clean: trash removal, bed making with your linens, surface wipe-downs. Laundry optional.

Office & Commercial Cleaning

Dusting, vacuuming/mopping, restroom sanitation, trash/recycling removal, break room/kitchen cleaning.

Read More

Grow Your Vision

At RMS Cleaning LLC, we are committed to providing superior, eco-friendly cleaning services that maintain the pristine condition of your spaces while prioritizing environmental sustainability.

As a family-owned business we’ve worked a strong commitment to excellence, we bring over a decade of expertise and unwavering dedication to every project we undertake. Whether you require residential cleaning or commercial cleaning services, our team of professionals is devoted to delivering exceptional, sustainable cleaning solutions tailored to your specific needs

Read More

Testimonials

Jayson Eniore New York

RMS Cleaning has been a game-changer for my business. Their attention to detail and reliability means I can focus on running my business without worrying about cleanliness. They are always on time and their team is very trustworthy. Absolutely the best cleaning service in Trenton!

Louis Pete New York

I hired RMS Cleaning for a deep clean of my home before a big family event, and they exceeded my expectations. The attention to detail was incredible—my kitchen and bathrooms have never looked better. The staff was friendly and punctual. Will definitely use them again!

Andy B New York

We use RMS Cleaning for our commercial property, and their service is top-notch. The team is always professional and does a thorough job every time. Our office looks immaculate, and we’ve received compliments from clients about how clean it is. Great service at a reasonable price!

Marie Beaubrun New York

Made appt late Monday afternoon. The crew showed up weds morning. Three very respectful workers showed up with all gear and supplies needed They did the initial clean then went back thru and treated each spot until it was removed They also were very thorough with removing the odors. They were quick yet thorough and again super friendly. Would absolutely recommend

frequently Ask Question

What areas do you serve?

We only service New Jersey

Are you insured?

Yes, RMS Cleaning is fully insured.

Do you bring supplies?

Yes, we provide all professional-grade supplies and equipment.

Do recurring clients get a discount?

Yes, recurring clients receive a discount on our standard rates.

Do you offer steam cleaning or hoarder cleanings?

Yes, we offer both steam cleaning and hoarder cleaning services.

How do I get a quote?

Send your address, # of beds & baths, cleaning type, and photos via text (267) 641-5137 or email. Quotes returned same day.

Are you available 24/7?

Yes, we’re on call 24/7, though we do not work Fri night or Sat until after sunset.

Can I book a weekend cleaning?

Yes, Sat evenings and all day Sun. Unavailable Sat morning & afternoon.

I’m a federal client—how do I arrange services?

Federal clients should email or call RMS Cleaning to discuss contract terms and scheduling.

Contact Us

Phone

(267) 641-5137

Email

rmscleaning0@gmail.com

On call 24/7

service scheduled Mon–Fri (any time), Sat evenings after sunset, Sun anytime.

About Us

About Us

At RMS Cleaning LLC, we are committed to providing superior, eco-friendly cleaning services that maintain the pristine condition of your spaces while prioritizing environmental sustainability. As a family-owned business with a strong commitment to excellence, we bring over a decade of expertise and unwavering dedication to every project we undertake. Whether you require residential cleaning or commercial cleaning services, our team of professionals is devoted to delivering exceptional, sustainable cleaning solutions tailored to your specific needs

Our Story

RMS Cleaning is a distinguished family-owned cleaning business Established in 2017 based in New Jersey. RMS Cleaning is dedicated to providing reliable, high-quality cleaning services with a strong focus on customer satisfaction and competitive pricing. The company offers a comprehensive range of services, including residential, commercial, deep cleaning, and move-in/move-out cleaning, all utilizing eco-friendly products. RMS Cleaning guarantees customer satisfaction, offering a complimentary follow-up visit if any areas are not cleaned to the clients expectations after the initial service and payment. For inquiries or to schedule a service, please contact RMS Cleaning at (609) 551-6636 or rmscleaning0@gmail.com.

RMS Cleaning was founded with a simple yet powerful mission: to provide exceptional cleaning services that exceed our clients expectations while prioritizing environmental sustainability. The inspiration to start this business came from recognizing the need for reliable and eco-friendly cleaning solutions in New Jersey. As a family-owned business, we have always valued the importance of cleanliness and the positive impact it has on peoples lives and well-being. Our journey began with a small team of dedicated professionals who shared a common vision of delivering top-quality cleaning services. Over the years, our commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction has allowed us to grow steadily. We have expanded our range of services to include residential cleaning, commercial cleaning, deep cleaning, and move-in/move-out cleaning, all while maintaining our focus on using eco-friendly products and practices.

Testimonials

Testimonials

Jayson Eniore New York

RMS Cleaning has been a game-changer for my business. Their attention to detail and reliability means I can focus on running my business without worrying about cleanliness. They are always on time and their team is very trustworthy. Absolutely the best cleaning service in Trenton!

Louis Pete New York

I hired RMS Cleaning for a deep clean of my home before a big family event, and they exceeded my expectations. The attention to detail was incrediblemy kitchen and bathrooms have never looked better. The staff was friendly and punctual. Will definitely use them again!

Andy B New York

We use RMS Cleaning for our commercial property, and their service is top-notch. The team is always professional and does a thorough job every time. Our office looks immaculate, and weve received compliments from clients about how clean it is. Great service at a reasonable price!

Marie Beaubrun New York

Made appt late Monday afternoon. The crew showed up weds morning. Three very respectful workers showed up with all gear and supplies needed They did the initial clean then went back thru and treated each spot until it was removed They also were very thorough with removing the odors. They were quick yet thorough and again super friendly. Would absolutely recommend
